				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>Thanks! I have a habit of making sentences full of semi-colons, colons, parentheses and em-dashes, sometimes all at once, and then being completely happy with it all while I&#8217;m editing. I should put money into a piggy-bank every time I use something that isn&#8217;t a comma or a full-stop.</p>
				</div><!-- .comment-content -->

