				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>I enjoyed the sense of journeying and capturing of memories.  In a way, it reminds me of the life of people who are always searching for something, never content with the present.</p>
				</div><!-- .comment-content -->

				<div class="reply"><a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='http://localhost:8888/microfiction.co.za/2011/02/20/making-an-escape/?replytocom=1251#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm( "div-comment-1251", "1251", "respond", "749" )' aria-label='Reply to nantalith'>Reply</a></div>			</article><!-- .comment-body -->
